				\begin{document}$$\begin{array}{l} \left\langle S \right\rangle = N \left\langle x \right\rangle \\\\ \sigma ^2 \{ S\} = N \left\langle {x^2 } \right\rangle \\ \end{array}$$\end{document}

This can also be written as\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
